name: TRENDY GANG X CLOT SOULJAHZ V2

metadata.name: CLOT SOULJAHZ V2 No. 1
metadata.description: TRENDY GANG is an expandable world which invites every diversity as long as they have style. Come to a world where you don't fight with your fists but fight to the beautiful end with your endless swag and your TOO FLY clique. Features from backgrounds, accessories and outfits of the characters are variable and upgradable to feature real world items. The first TRENDY GANG is the CLOT SOULJAHZ, repping their international Asian set with style flair and heritage. Enjoy growing your crew and staying fly till the day you die as all members of the TRENDY GANG usually do.
